mment\\\">// 缓冲数组</span>\\n        <span class=\\\"hljs-keyword\\\">transient</span> Object[] elementData; <span class=\\\"hljs-comment\\\">// non-private to simplify nested class access</span>\\n        <span class=\\\"hljs-comment\\\">// ArrayList 的大小（它包含的元素数）。</span>\\n        <span class=\\\"hljs-keyword\\\">private</span> <span class=\\\"hljs-type\\\">int</span> s', '{\"code\":200,\"msg\":\"操作成功\",\"data\":null}', 0, '', '2022-10-01 21:26:12');
