ng>写入</strong>它。</span></p></li><li class=\\\"md-list-item\\\"><p style=\\\"line-height: 1.6rem\\\" class=\\\"md-end-block md-p\\\"><span>它有三个概念：</span><code>state</code><span>、</span><code>getter</code><span>、</span><code>action</code><span>，相当于组件中的： </span><code>data</code><span>、 </span><code>computed</code><span> 和 </span><code>methods</code><span>。</span></p></li><li class=\\', '{\"code\":200,\"msg\":\"操作成功\",\"data\":{\"uuid\":null,\"fabulousCount\":0,\"fansFabulousCount\":0,\"collectionCount\":0,\"followCount\":0,\"fansFollowCount\":0,\"commentCount\":0,\"fansCommentCount\":0,\"articleCount\":0,\"specialColumnCount\":0,\"fansSpecialColumn\":0,\"circleCount\":0,\"albumCount\":0,\"dictumCount\":0,\"id\":59,\"userId\":null,\"articleTitle\":null,\"articleCover\":null,\"articleAbstract\":null,\"articleContent\":null,\"theme\":null,\"type\":null,\"reprintUrl\":null,\"state\":null,\"updateId\":null,\"specialId\":null,\"collectionId\":null,\"collectionRecordId\":null,\"groupingId\":null,\"groupingName\":null,\"labelId\":null,\"labelList\":null,\"labelNameList\":null,\"labelLongList\":null,\"likeTimes\":0,\"fabulousUserSet\":null,\"isCollection\":null,\"collectionRId\":null,\"commentTimes\":0,\"collectionTimes\":0,\"numberTimes\":0,\"isPublic\":null,\"auditState\":null,\"auditTime\":null,\"updateTime\":null,\"createTime\":null,\"heatWeight\":0,\"occupation\":null,\"username\":null,\"nickname\":null,\"avatar\":null,\"isFollow\":false,\"buttonLoading\":false}}', 0, '', '2024-11-17 23:36:46');
